content: Hello Mari, nice to meet you. I'm the hiring officer for the Software Engineer position at Google.
That's great! Can you tell me more about some of the projects you've worked on? What technologies did you use and what were your responsibilities?
Can you share some specific details about one of the projects you're most proud of, and what your role was in it? What did you learn from the experience?
That's impressive, Mari! Can you tell me more about the company you interned with and what your responsibilities were during the internship? What skills or knowledge did you gain from the experience?
